    "text": {
      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">People</a> * Niklas Fiekas</b>\n</p><p><b>Niklas Fiekas</b>,<br />\na German chess player and aficionado, open source software developer <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>, and computer scientist affiliated with <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Clausthal_University_of_Technology\">Clausthal University of Technology</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> . He is primary author of <a href=\"/Python-chess\" title=\"Python-chess\">python-chess</a>, a chess library written in <a href=\"/Python\" title=\"Python\">Python</a> featuring <a href=\"/Move_Generation\" title=\"Move Generation\">move generation</a> and validation, <a href=\"/Portable_Game_Notation\" title=\"Portable Game Notation\">PGN</a> reading <sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> and <a href=\"/Opening_Book\" title=\"Opening Book\">opening book</a> reading.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Selected_Publications\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Selected Publications</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Forum_Posts\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Forum Posts</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#2015_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2015 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#2020_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2020 ...</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Selected_Publications\">Selected Publications</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Niklas_Fiekas&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Selected Publications\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Niklas Fiekas</a> (<b>2020</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://backscattering.de/chess/hashtable-packing/\">The Hashtable Packing Problem</a></i>. (Draft)</li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Forum_Posts\">Forum Posts</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Niklas_Fiekas&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: Forum Posts\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2015_...\">2015 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Niklas_Fiekas&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: 2015 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=58262\">Why is there a PGN SetUp tag?</a> by Niklas Fiekas, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, November 15, 2015</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=58488\">Syzygy probing code: DTZ in some cursed endgames off by one?</a> by Niklas Fiekas, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, December 06, 2015</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=61832\">Suicide chess tablebases (stalemated player wins)</a> by Niklas Fiekas, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, October 25, 2016&#160;» <a href=\"/Losing_Chess\" title=\"Losing Chess\">Losing Chess</a>, <a href=\"/Syzygy_Bases\" title=\"Syzygy Bases\">Syzygy Bases</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=65187\">Disproving the existence of some magics</a> by Niklas Fiekas, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, September 16, 2017&#160;» <a href=\"/Looking_for_Magics\" title=\"Looking for Magics\">Looking for Magics</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=67051\">No bishop magics with fixed shift 8</a> by Niklas Fiekas, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, April 09, 2018</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2020_...\">2020 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Niklas_Fiekas&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: 2020 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=73071\">Hashtable packing (e.g. to optimize magic bitboards) is strongly NP-complete</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Niklas Fiekas</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>,  February 13, 2020&#160;» <a href=\"/Magic_Bitboards\" title=\"Magic Bitboards\">Magic Bitboards</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Niklas_Fiekas&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://github.com/niklasf\">niklasf (Niklas Fiekas) · GitHub</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://github.com/niklasf/python-chess\">niklasf/python-chess · GitHub</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://backscattering.de/\">backscattering.de</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.drupal.org/user/1089248\">Niklas Fiekas | Drupal.org</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://twitter.com/niklasfiekas?lang=de\">Niklas Fiekas (@NiklasFiekas) / Twitter</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://ratings.fide.com/card.phtml?event=16215338\">Fiekas, Niklas FIDE Chess Profile</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Niklas_Fiekas&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://osrc.dfm.io/niklasf/\">Niklas Fiekas's Open Source Report Card</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://tu-clausthal.academia.edu/NiklasFiekas\">Niklas Fiekas | Clausthal University of Technology - Academia.edu</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-3\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=54779&amp;start=4\">Re: PGN to FEN (with Evaluation)?</a> by <a href=\"/Matthew_Lai\" title=\"Matthew Lai\">Matthew Lai</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, December 29, 2014</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-4\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Strong_NP-completeness\">Strong NP-completeness from Wikipedia</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-5\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Drupal\">Drupal from Wikipedia</a></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n<p><b><a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">Up one Level</a></b>\n</p>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260228153523\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.014 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.015 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 97/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 206/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 0/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 0/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 2/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    0.000      1 -total\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key oscar70_mw1-mw_:pcache:idhash:100-0!canonical and timestamp 20260228153523 and revision id 19676\n -->\n"
